                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-960-18350406 t18350406-960-punishment-85"></join>Confined Two Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Gaselee</hi>.</p>
